OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud will
OL,6,Fcontinue to thicken this evening as
OL,7,Fthe rain turns heavier through the
OL,8,Fnight. Staying breezy and mild under
OL,9,Fthe thick blanket of cloud. Rain
OL,10,Fbecomes patchier and lighter by dawn
OL,11,Fbut staying cloudy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FBreezy and cloudy with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of drizzle at first, and
OL,15,Fperhaps a few brighter spells. Rain
OL,16,Fwill turn heavier for a time in the
OL,17,Fafternoon, before clearing to the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
